title.narrative: Regional Project: Partnership for Innovations (Next Generation)

description.narrative: This activity's goal is to strengthen civil society within Central Asia in a manner that is both sustainable and inclusive within and across national boundaries fostering progress and sustainability. USAID support has been instrumental in mobilizing civil society coalitions to challenge regressive NGO bills and laws - many modeled on Russian legislation.
